description: The finest Ribs, brisket, pulled pork, and smoked chicken that you can get in the state of Oklahoma. Our S.O.B. (Smokin' Okies Burrito) is one of the most unique way to eat pulled pork. All of our food is made fresh daily inside the trailer, even our side dishes. Our potato casserole is a speciality side dish you will not find in any other restuarant, along with our pinto's with a kick.
name: Smokin' Okies Mobile BBQ Smokehouse
